Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:46.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can I see those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:48.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I a weirdo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:50.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:51.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:55.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:58.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You live around here, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:00.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:02.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you around often.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:05.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:07.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:09.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see them too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.05,0:02:10.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Those strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:24.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Natsume in this class?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:28.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:29.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if he's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have much of a presence, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:34.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:35.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there, the one by the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:37.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:39.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:44.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:47.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got... a guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:49.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:58.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He was asking for you just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:02:59.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see him around much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:06.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for waking you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:07.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:10.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, you sure sleep a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't sleep at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:14.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:16.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got some problems, I'll listen to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:17.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:20.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The chime has already rung.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:40.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I inherited my grandmother's Book of Friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:45.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Youkai have been coming to reclaim their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:55.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike my grandmother, I gladly return their life-valued names. {re-edit this}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:59.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm going to break down...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:04.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:08.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go, Nyanko-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:11.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You reek of alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:13.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:17.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you back a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:19.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:27.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:30.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on home, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:33.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get captured by that stupid cat again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damned cursed brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:40.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Takashi-kun! I'm going shopping now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:41.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:42.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:47.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your day off, so you don't need to stay home. You can go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you made new friends here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're all very friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:55.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:57.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:08.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A bug, a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:13.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Natsume-sama, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive us for intruding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:17.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:19.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive us for intruding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:21.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're returning their names again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:27.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, the Book of Friends is getting thinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:30.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm waiting for the day when a huge one which he will not be able to handle to arrive,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and eat this cheeky brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nyanko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:38.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do all these small Youkai keep coming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like them small?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:42.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:47.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to Natsume-sama because he has immense power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:51.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us, Natsume-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:56.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a human that we would like you to exterminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Human extermination?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:06:03.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A pretentious, human Youkai exterminator has recently come to our dwelling place, the Eight Fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:08.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But rather than extermination, the human just seems to be testing his power and enjoying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:12.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just trying to live happily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:15.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there really humans who can exterminate Youkai, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:19.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us, Natsume-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:23.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you don't know, but there are problems when a human exterminates another human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:28.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:31.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it sound interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:35.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing humans is my specialty, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Things will get complicated, so please be quiet, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.91,0:06:42.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A Youkai exterminator, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:46.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means they believe in those things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they can see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:51.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see them too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:00.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going no-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still there, sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:06.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:08.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:10.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step aside! Step Aside!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:13.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step aside! Step Aside!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Natsume-sama is passing through!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:17.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move down! Move down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move down! Move down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:19.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step aside! Step Aside!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:22.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:26.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no, it's been shown to be because of my back's proportion!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:30.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He won't let us see him off and pick him up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:32.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, it's a real bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so this is school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:37.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,School, school!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:38.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:44.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume! Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:48.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should write over there too! Should we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:48.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38\bord1.3}Sign - Charm
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:49.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:09.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:13.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll at least listen to your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:23.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thank you, Natsume-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What kind of people are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:32.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They always shoot a spirit wave out of the blue, so we can't get close,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:34.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,or see them well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They smell human, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:37.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:40.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they have a grudge or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:46.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're easily affected by Youkai and are not used to having them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:54.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, I'd rather talk to them than these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:01.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:02.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You came again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:08.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you said you could see them too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:10.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:15.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:17.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:19.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A human? There's a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:30.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn human!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to drive us out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:34.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:36.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanko-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:38.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:40.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:41.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all small ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:44.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You should learn how to exorcise them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to blast them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:49.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't hurry, they'll suck your brain through the holes of your nose and ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:51.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you damn sexual harassing Youkai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:56.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sexual harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:58.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:02.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It means a sexy belly dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:06.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to make them stop, you damn sadistic cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:11.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? I can hear something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:18.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:20.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here! It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:22.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:23.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab hold, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:34.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ones with a high spiritual power are able to shoot a purifying wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:38.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They aimed at an open field and shot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:39.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A purifying wave...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:53.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Was everyone erased?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:55.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They just ran in fright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:02.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This place has been purified though, so the low level ones won't be coming back for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:05.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So they were chased out of their place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:07.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A sudden attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:09.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who is doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:14.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting into it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:17.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So will you do it, Natsume-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:18.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:22.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you couldn't come back here for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:25.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both different types!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:28.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then can't you do something about it yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:32.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:42.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I'm getting more involved with the Youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:45.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If I open up to them too much again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:47.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You look sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:50.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:51.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:52.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:11:59.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That glance just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:04.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you know that guy who just passed by?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:07.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Class 1's Tanuma, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:13.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one that asked for you the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:17.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He just moved in to that old temple just past the Eight Fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight Fields?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:23.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:28.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Tanuma is the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:35.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There might not be another who can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:40.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no one who could understand the fear of walking alone in this unstable world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is different from what we promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:46.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Look after him next month! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:49.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeding my family alone is a trial!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:52.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, he keeps saying creepy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he can see strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:06.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:08.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They said I'm not their family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:10.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's obvious, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lonely, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:24.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel lonely now that you've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:26.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:28.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:30.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see them too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:34.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not strange, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:36.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:40.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't Takashi-kun from next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:43.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:48.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There might not be another who can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:50.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,In this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:52.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Unstable world...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:59.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, what's wrong Takashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:00.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:02.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:05.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:08.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:13.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He lives in the Eight Fields neighborhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:15.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know his address?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:17.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:21.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought it was unusual for you to be interested in someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:22.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:23.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:27.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Tanuma are similar in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:29.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You two like being alone, suddenly becoming uneasy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:33.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and your faces go pale as if you're seeing something scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:38.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Youkai exterminator is probably Tanuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He can probably see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:45.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, he's the first one like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:46.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:48.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:50.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Chukyuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:52.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We got hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:53.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A direct hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The exterminator came again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:58.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's most likely still in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:00.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:04.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, as long as we rest and absorb power from the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:07.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if they can see them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How can they do something terrible like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:14.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't all good, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:20.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:29.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:31.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:32.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come to see Natsume-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:37.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a cheeky face just like Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the Book of Friends, do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:41.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like my name returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:44.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could we do that later?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit busy at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:47.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:49.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Planning how to exterminate a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:50.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I, Misuzu, shall help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:16:00.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Having my name stolen and not being able to serve my master at least once is dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:01.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:04.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The one from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:09.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have saved my servant the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:12.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What a good thing you did, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:14.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be quiet, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:20.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from Natsume-sama! You command someone as great as Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Book of Friends is to be feared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:24.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to suck up to me all the time. {... replaces "for everything"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:28.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-dono! Natsume-sama's enemy, the human, is in that forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please punish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:33.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:34.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:39.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. This is bad, bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:42.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If something that strong faces the exterminator,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:45.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanuma might die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find him first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:51.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:03.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop, stop, stop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Give him an order, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:06.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Say his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:27.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn amateur!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:36.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as their names are in the Book of Friends, you can end things quickly by ordering them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:41.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:46.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Tanuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:50.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Youkai exterminator?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Natsume-sama! Finish him off quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish him! Finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:58.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, this is him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:00.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's his smell, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:01.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:03.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:07.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking to yourself about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:12.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He can't see the Youkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:17.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I just moved in to the temple at the Eight Fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:20.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, my son is quite sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:23.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So he gets affected by things easily and often gets sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:28.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I heard that this area was known for having monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:33.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So I would often go around and purify the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just to soothe them, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:36.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Soothe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:40.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He has such power and he can't see us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:44.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than having spiritual power, he seems to have Buddhist powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:49.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't born with the power, so he trained and learned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:52.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he still can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:56.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The monsters around here probably aren't very bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:58.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,so please keep it to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:02.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be you can see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:11.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't need to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:15.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to talk, please come by anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:20.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You might get along well with my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:21.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Son?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:24.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Priest, what is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:27.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Tanuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:41.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite what you say, you seem to favor the Ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:45.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm partial to them or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:49.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that we exchanged words and became acquaintances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:54.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was small, there was even a Youkai who took on the form of a human just to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:59.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a kid, so my actions may have hurt them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:02.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:04.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:07.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:14.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I'm glad to have met them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:17.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:19.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:24.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see some strange things in the garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:24.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:30.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But for a moment, I felt like I saw the shadows of two strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:36.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably just seeing things again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:40.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I would see shadows and feel some presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:43.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for talking about weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:48.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a rumor that some Natsume guy would seem like he sometimes saw things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's probably my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:55.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see very weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:01.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:05.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We might just be the weird ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:07.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it well,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:17.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've come to understand something recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:20.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you're a human or an Ayakashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:22.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,we're the same in that we meet with our hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:26.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,that being alone is lonely,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:28.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and that the first step is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:38.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-dono, I would like my name returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:42.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm tired today, so make it another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:47.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And just as usual, my days are troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.02,0:21:50.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get along well with Youkai,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:52.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:04.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But, listening to them sometimes might be nice.
